{"tid":1535850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打見過？杏花邨地鐵站","createTime":"2019-09-03T13:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:54:28.000Z","uid":222900,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18cb93798fde19b79600267b077d466497c5c2c7","tid":1535850,"uid":222900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"話說夜晚做完gym就番屋企啦，7點4左右啦～<br />\n咁到左地鐵站，就有個講普通話嘅女人問我野啦，<br />\n幾有禮貌，正正常常熟女樣，不是年輕嗰隻啦至少，<br />\n咁我普通話唔太好，靜係聽到咩呢度無街道乜鬼咁，<br />\n然後話佢朋友5天後先落泥香港，佢無「零錢」（應該硬幣意思啦），<br />\n叫我俾現金她，咁嗰下覺得無咩野就話直接買野食俾佢啦，<br />\n我都知我蠢左，不過當下真係覺得無問題，<br />\n因為一來病病哋，二來又做完gym好攰好眼訓，<br />\n但我都唔會直接俾錢佢，佢話微信俾番錢我，<br />\n我話唔洗啦，<br />\n咁我就建議她響地鐵站間OK便利店俾佢自己揀野食，<br />\n入去前佢叫我唔好響收銀員面前講佢無錢買，要俾下面子佢，<br />\n我話好，<br />\n但結果，佢買左個包無問題，但重點點解要買兩排3粒金莎呢？<br />\n嗰下我就知被騙啦😂😂，至少感覺怪怪地，<br />\n不過我講得出做得到，無講岀泥，<br />\n我講到呢度可能你會笑，<br />\n叫做提下大家睇下有無人都同樣遇過呢個人啦，<br />\n同埋日後小心謹慎啦，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然要一個女人問人攞野食借錢都要一定嘅勇氣，<br />\n唔係無錢都唔洗咁，i mean 有米嘅有正職嘅都唔洗問人借，<br />\n不過我好似番到屋企望番番去地鐵站又見到佢，<br />\n公平啲，太遠，唔肯定係咪佢。<br />\n<br />\n希望她今晚最後一晚咁做啦，以後生活幸福唔洗再問人攞啦～"},{"pid":"ffba7e52949997ff295ad35200a0d6514b47a1d8","tid":1535850,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"十點鳩叫行動！！！！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Av5cBad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAv5cBad.jpg&h=53535c10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4pT43z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4pT43z.jpg&h=df08fc7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH9T43A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH9T43A.jpg&h=5ee30c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04MOTWW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04MOTWW.png&h=5666d4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eL579vg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeL579vg.jpg&h=3a5dd848&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8950d9f5969a623b2eb4addbdced26ca0442ff67","tid":1535850,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2ee52cccb5dfbba015f23fb87936980cc790e2e","tid":1535850,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為一來病病哋，二來又做完gym好攰好眼訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都關事？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c859ab30d3a82410e0ec0c79cbe92c00cf6cce9b","tid":1535850,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:43:59.000Z","msg"